Creates a empty errorLst object

Source: R/getEmptyErrorLst.R
getEmptyErrorLst.Rd

Creates a empty errorLst object

Usage

getEmptyErrorLst()

Value

An errorLst object with placeholders for error types found in a pedigree file by qcStudbook.

Examples

# \donttest{
library(nprcgenekeepr)
getEmptyErrorLst()

#>
